Package org.jamsim.ascape.weights

Weighting related classes.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
WeightCalculator An Observable ParameterSets that calculates a weight when provided with a variable map.
 

Class Summary
CategoricalVarAdjTableModel A casper container table model with but the first column editable, and auto adjustment for each row.
CategoricalVarAdjustment Displays levels of a categorical variable across potentially multiple iterations and allows user to specify a proportion for each cell.
CategoricalVarWCTableModel Table Model for the weighting of a categorical variable.
CategoricalVarWeightCalc Calculates weights for each factor level of a single variable.
ContinuousVarAdjTableModel TableModel for the adjustment of a continuous variable.
ContinuousVarAdjustment Displays levels of a continuous variable and allows user to add an amount to each level.
